:HELP NAME=OMH012GEN.Customer Contact Maintenance - Help
:XH3.Customer Contact Maintenance
:ISCH ROOTS='customer contact maintenance'.
Customer Contact Maintenance

:P.
The customer contact maintenance function enables you to define
and maintain the contacts who are allowed to call the HelpDesk
on behalf of the customer. You are able to define an unlimited
number of contacts per customer.

:P.
You can enter your contacts in the
database along with some specific data. If you want more information
about an attribute, move the cursor to the attribute area
and press help. If you want more information about contacts in
general, please follow this link to the
:LINK PERFORM='DSPHELP CONCUSC OMSCONHD'.
customer concepts.
:ELINK.
:EHELP.

