:HELP NAME='OMH01201/FMOPT1'.Option - Help

:XH3.Option field
:P.
These are the list options. The options all act on a
specific list entry. The following options are available;

:PARML.
:PT.2=Change
:PD.
Use option 2 to change the contact.
:PT.4=Delete
:PD.
Use option 4 to remove the contact. The contact can not be removed
if there are call tracks for this contact. Be also aware of the
fact that the templates for this contact will be removed as well.
:PT.5=Display
:PD.
Use option 5 to view the contact definition.
:EPARML.
